---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Venture — Updates & Goals">
  <section class="section">
    <p class="kicker">Updates</p>
    <h1 class="h1">Pilots & Roadmap</h1>
    <p class="lead">We’re preparing classroom pilots and collecting educator feedback to improve the kit and resources.</p>
    <div class="hr"></div>
    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="">
        <h2 class="h2">Near‑term goals</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Deploy pilot kits to partner classrooms and STEM clubs</li>
          <li>Measure learning outcomes and activity timing</li>
          <li>Refine lesson plans and answer keys from teacher input</li>
          <li>Stress‑test components for durability and easier cleanup</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="">
        <h2 class="h2">What’s next</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Publish downloadable teacher materials</li>
          <li>Set up online ordering and managed fulfillment</li>
          <li>Open educator community for tips and variations</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="" style="margin-top:1rem">
      <p class="muted" style="margin:0">If you’d like to pilot the kit, contact us via the form — we’ll follow up with details.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>


